5. Food:papaya == Beverage:coffee
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Flower:amaryllis
7. Food:radish == Cigar:dunhill
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Music-Genre:r&b is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Flower:dahlia
11. Flower:tulips is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:peasmaster == Beverage:beer
13. Music-Genre:soul == Cigar:prince
14. Music-Genre:r&b is on the left or right of Food:peas
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Beverage:water

